data.description: Welcome home to 511 Killdeer located in the highly desirable Nexton North Creek Village. This meticulously maintained home is better than new. Upgraded kitchen countertops, cabinets & tile backsplash are accentuated by the upgraded light fixtures and ceiling fans. The owners added extra windows which beam in natural light. The downstairs office could be a 4th bedroom and the upstairs bonus room could be a 5th bedroom. The primary bedroom features a large walk in closet and the bathroom features an upgraded shower with dual vanity & soaking tub. Outside you can enjoy the fully fenced backyard and patio with pergola. The added stone work around the front porch is just the cherry on top. Schedule your showing before it's gone!
